  },
  {
    "Id": 5,
    "Content": "```C++\nnamespace add::test\n{\n    /**\n     * My function, add two integer.\n     * @param a arg a, int type\n     * @param b arg b, int type\n     * @return int type, will a + b\n     * @module add.test.add\n     */\n    int add(int a, int b);\n}\n```",
    "ContentSha": "/l7c+f25PcRtwwR3okA0xOhls5bJ9m0Zo288Po4znwQ=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```C++\nnamespace add::test\n{\n    /**\n     * My function, add two integer.\n     * @param a arg a, int type\n     * @param b arg b, int type\n     * @return int type, will a + b\n     * @module add.test.add\n     */\n    int add(int a, int b);\n}\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 6,
    "Content": "其中第一行为函数介绍,@param为参数介绍,@return为返回值介绍(可空)\n如果只需要编译并打包为whl文件则无需修改main.cpp\n使用python project build即可开始编译并打包whl文件\n编译后安装whl后即可在直接直接调用:",
    "ContentSha": "wzsRkrKWRO88Tn87mo82el4ZZqDtgqYUvp/31QtnuPg=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
